======================= README for RubyES-186 =========================

RubyES stands for RubyEnterpriseServer and is pronounced "Roo - Bees".

=======================================================================

Step #1 - Run the "install.sh" script as a regular (non root) user

Step #2 - Source the Ruby Environment file ( . ./rubyEnv.sh )

Step #3 - Enjoy the Power of Roooo-Beeeeees!!

----- open source components -----

gem install merb
gem install passenger
passenger-install-apache2-module
git clone git://github.com/drogus/apache-upload-progress-module.git
cd apache-upload-progress-module/
/usr/sbin/apxs -c -i -a mod_upload_progress.c
